{"title":"Quadratische Gleichungen","markdown":{"headingText":"Formen","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"{{< include _includes/_front_matter.qmd >}}\n{{< include _includes/_init_fontawesome.qmd >}} \n{{< include _includes/_katex_macros.qmd >}} \n{{< include _includes/_r_themes.qmd >}}\n\n\n## Column\n\n::: {.card title=\"Allgemeine Form\" fill=\"true\" .text-success .text-bg-success .bg-opacity-10}\n\n**Vollständige Form**\n\n$$\nax^2 + bx + c = 0\n$$\n\nKoeffizienten: $a$, $b$, $c$\n\nStreckfaktor: $a$\n\nWenn $a \\neq 0$\n\n$$\nx^2 + \\frac{b}{a}x + \\frac{c}{a} = 0\n$$\n\n<br>\n\n**Abgeleitete lineare Formen**\n\n| $a$ | $b$ | $c$ | Gleichung |\n|---- |---- |---- |---- |\n| $=0$ | $=0$ | $\\neq 0$ | $c = 0$, Falsch! |\n| $=0$ | $\\neq 0$ | $=0$ | $bx = 0$ |\n| $=0$ | $\\neq 0$ | $\\neq 0$ | $bx + c = 0$ |\n: {.light}\n\n**Abgeleitete quadratische Formen**\n\n| $a$ | $b$ | $c$ | Gleichung |\n|---- |---- |---- |---- |\n| $\\neq 0$ | $=0$ | $=0$ | $ax^2 = 0$ |\n| $\\neq 0$ | $=0$ | $\\neq 0$ | $ax^2 + c = 0$ |\n| $\\neq 0$ | $\\neq 0$ | $=0$ | $ax^2 + bx = 0$ |\n: {.light}\n\n:::\n\n## Column\n\n::: {.card title=\"Normalform\" fill=\"true\" .text-info .text-bg-info .bg-opacity-10}\n\n$$\nx^2 + px + q = 0\n$$\n\nKoeffizienten: $p$, $q$\n\n:::\n\n## Column\n\n::: {.card title=\"Nullstellenform\" fill=\"true\" .text-warning .text-bg-warning .bg-opacity-10}\n\n$$\na \\cdot (x - x_1) \\cdot (x - x_2) = 0\n$$\n\nNullstellen: $x_1$, $x_2$\n\nStreckfaktor: $a$\n\n:::\n\n# Beziehungen\n\n## Column\n\n::: {.card title=\"Beziehungen und Umwandlungen\" fill=\"false\" .text-danger .text-bg-background .bg-opacity-10}\n\nEs ist nur der Hinweg zur Normalform gezeigt. Der Rückweg ist auch möglich, wenn alle mathematischen Schritte umgekehrt ablaufen.\n\n```{dot}\ngraph {\n  A -- B\n}\n```\n\n```{mermaid}\n%%| mermaid-format: svg\n%%| fig-responsive: true\n%%| fig-height: 6\n\nflowchart TD\n    classDef text_success shape:rounded,color:#3f6d3c,fill:#F4F4E7,stroke:#F4F4E7;\n    classDef text_info shape:rounded,color:#356087,fill:#F4F4E7,stroke:#F4F4E7;\n    classDef text_warning shape:rounded,color:#8c40b8,fill:#F4F4E7,stroke:#F4F4E7;\n    classDef text_danger shape:rounded,color:#6c7028,fill:#F4F4E7,stroke:#F4F4E7;\n    classDef empty height:0,width:0;\n\n    General(\"$$ax^2+bx+c=0$$\"):::text_success\n    GeneralAoutBC(\"$$a\\left(x^2+\\frac{b}{a}x+\\frac{c}{a}\\right)=0$$\"):::text_success\n    NormalABC(\"$$x^2+\\frac{b}{a}x+\\frac{c}{a}=0$$\"):::text_info\n    NormalPQ(\"$$x^2+px+q=0$$\"):::text_info\n    GeneralLinearRoots(\"$$a \\cdot (x - x_1) \\cdot (x - x_2) = 0$$\"):::text_warning\n    GeneralRoots(\"$$a \\cdot \\left[ x^2 - \\left( x_1 + x_2 \\right) x + x_1 x_2 \\right] = 0$$\"):::text_warning\n    NormalLinearRoots(\"$$(x - x_1) \\cdot (x - x_2) = 0$$\"):::text_warning\n    NormalRoots(\"$$x^2 - \\left( x_1 + x_2 \\right) x + x_1 x_2 = 0$$\"):::text_info\n    \n    General -->|\"<p>$$\\;\\textcolor{#6c7028}{\\cdot\\frac{1}{a}}\\;$$</p>\"| NormalABC\n    NormalABC -->|\"<p>$$\\;\\textcolor{#6c7028}{p=\\frac{b}{a},\\;q=\\frac{c}{a}}\\;$$</p>\"| NormalPQ\n\n    GeneralLinearRoots -->|Distributivgesetz| GeneralRoots\n    GeneralRoots -->|\"<p>$$\\;\\textcolor{#6c7028}{\\frac{b}{a}=-(x_1+x_2),\\;\\frac{c}{a}=x_1 x_2}\\;$$</p>\"| GeneralAoutBC\n    GeneralAoutBC -->|Distributivgesetz| General\n\n    GeneralLinearRoots -->|\"<p>$$\\;\\textcolor{#6c7028}{\\cdot\\frac{1}{a}}\\;$$</p>\"| NormalLinearRoots\n    NormalLinearRoots -->|Distributivgesetz| NormalRoots\n    NormalRoots -->|\"<p>$$\\;\\textcolor{#6c7028}{p=-(x_1+x_2),\\;q=x_1 x_2}\\;$$</p>\"| NormalPQ\n\n    linkStyle 0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7 stroke:#6C7028,stroke-width:3px;\n```\n\n:::\n\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"mathdash-dashboard":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"mathdash-dashboard","base-format":"dashboard","extension-name":"mathdash"},"execute":{"fig-width":8,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":tru